## Purpose and Intent

This repository contains my personal solutions to Boot.dev's [Learn Cryptography with Golang](https://www.boot.dev/courses/learn-cryptography-golang) course. These materials are shared strictly for educational reference and learning purposes only.

## Repository Contents

This repository includes two categories of files with different ownership:

### My Original Work (solution files)
- **`main.go`** files in each chapter/level directory — these are my own original solutions, written by me

### Third-Party Course Material (Boot.dev property)
- **`*_test.go`** and **`main_tests.go`** files — these are the intellectual property of Boot.dev and are included solely as the test harness required to validate and run my solutions locally
- **`helpers.go`** files — likewise owned by Boot.dev and included as course-provided scaffolding

**Boot.dev retains full copyright over all test files and helper files.** This repository makes no claim of ownership over those files. They are Boot.dev's property and subject to Boot.dev's terms and conditions.

